description: This file serves as the entry point for a React application. It imports React and ReactDOM libraries, as well as CSS styling and the main App component. It initializes the React root rendering process and mounts the App component within the DOM element with id 'root'.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for rendering React components into the DOM.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders React elements into the root DOM node.
